<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.10.4">
<l>peṇṇāṉāḷ pēriḷaṅ koṅkaiyi ṉāraḻalpōl</l>
<l>uṇṇānañ cuṇṭukan tāyai yukantēṉnāṉ</l>
<l>maṇṇāḷā. vāḷneṭuṅ kaṇṇi matumalarāḷ</l>
<l>kaṇṇāḷā kaṇṇa purattuṟai yammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I rejoiced in you who rejoiced, having eaten the inedible poison like fire</l>
<l>Which filled the large, young breasts of the one who became a woman,</l>
<l>Ruler of earth, husband of the lady of the honeyed blossom,</l>
<l>The one with long eyes like lances, lord who dwells in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
